welcome_message_body: "Welcome to Notteroy, where the charming blend of scenic beauty and friendly locals await you. Famous for its picturesque landscapes and rich cultural heritage, we invite you to discover and savor the wonders of our city."

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Sandefjord Airport handles all domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Cargo Terminal
terminals.description: The cargo terminal at Sandefjord Airport handles all cargo and freight operations.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport. No password is required.
